entries.femaleVariant: Been a while since I seen Trav.
You ain't heard? Flatlined a few days ago.
Gonk came 'cross this old can of God knows what sketch.
I told him, I was like, "Don't Trav, heard there's some weird-ass meat floatin' 'round town."
Gonk ain't listen. Ate it anyway.
Always was a brave spirit, our Trav.
"What if it's 'ganic? Like rat, rabbit, or whatever the fuck?"
